---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-32 bg-gray-900">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Why organisations work with us</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="bento-container">
      <div class="bento-section bento-section-large group">
        <div class="bento-body">
          <div class="bento-icon relative">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border-2 border-red-500/30 group-hover:animate-spin-slow transition-all duration-300"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-2 w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-red-400/50 group-hover:animate-pulse"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-4 w-16 h-16 bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-red-500/40">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-red-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-red-500/10 group-hover:animate-ping opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-content">
            <h3>Reduced Risk</h3>
            <p>We deliver in stages. You see progress early and avoid big-bang surprises.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-section bento-section-small group">
        <div class="bento-body">
          <div class="bento-icon relative">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border-2 border-green-500/30 group-hover:animate-spin-slow transition-all duration-300"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-2 w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-green-400/50 group-hover:animate-pulse"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-4 w-16 h-16 bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-green-500/40">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.623 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 group-hover:animate-ping opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-content">
            <h3>Security by Design</h3>
            <p>Data protection and access controls are built in from day one.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-section bento-section-small group">
        <div class="bento-body">
          <div class="bento-icon relative">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border-2 border-purple-500/30 group-hover:animate-spin-slow transition-all duration-300"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-2 w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-purple-400/50 group-hover:animate-pulse"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-4 w-16 h-16 bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-purple-500/40">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 group-hover:animate-ping opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-content">
            <h3>Reliable Delivery</h3>
            <p>Clear scope, fixed steps, and regular check-ins keep work on track.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-section bento-section-small group">
        <div class="bento-body">
          <div class="bento-icon relative">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border-2 border-orange-500/30 group-hover:animate-spin-slow transition-all duration-300"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-2 w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-orange-400/50 group-hover:animate-pulse"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-4 w-16 h-16 bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-orange-500/40">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-orange-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 7.996 21 8.625 21h6.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-6.75c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C21 20.496 20.496 21 19.875 21H4.125C3.504 21 3 20.496 3 19.875v-6.75z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 group-hover:animate-ping opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-content">
            <h3>Scales with You</h3>
            <p>Start small, prove value, then roll out without rework.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-section bento-section-small group">
        <div class="bento-body">
          <div class="bento-icon relative">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border-2 border-cyan-500/30 group-hover:animate-spin-slow transition-all duration-300"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-2 w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-cyan-400/50 group-hover:animate-pulse"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-4 w-16 h-16 bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-cyan-500/40">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-cyan-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 6h9.75M10.5 6a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 10-3 0M3.75 6H7.5m0 12h9.75m-9.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-3.75 0H7.5m0-9h9.75M7.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 10-3 0m-3.75 0H7.5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 group-hover:animate-ping opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-content">
            <h3>Flexible Engagement</h3>
            <p>On your stack, in our cloud, or a hybrid — whatever fits policy and cost.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-section bento-section-large group">
        <div class="bento-body">
          <div class="bento-icon relative">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border-2 border-pink-500/30 group-hover:animate-spin-slow transition-all duration-300"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-2 w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-pink-400/50 group-hover:animate-pulse"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-4 w-16 h-16 bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-pink-500/40">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-pink-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.19 8.688a4.5 4.5 0 011.242 7.244l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364-6.364l1.757-1.757m13.35-.622l1.757-1.757a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 001.242 7.244" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-pink-500/10 group-hover:animate-ping opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-content">
            <h3>Works With Your Tools</h3>
            <p>We integrate with common meeting, messaging, and project platforms to cut friction.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bento-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-auto-rows: minmax(180px, auto);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bento-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto;
    }
  }

  .bento-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8) 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9) 100%);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .bento-section-large {
    grid-column: span 2;
    grid-row: span 1;
  }

  .bento-section-medium {
    grid-column: span 2;
    grid-row: span 1;
  }

  .bento-section-small {
    grid-column: span 1;
    grid-row: span 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bento-section-large,
    .bento-section-medium,
    .bento-section-small {
      grid-column: span 1;
      grid-row: span 1;
      min-height: 200px;
    }
  }

  .bento-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15), transparent 50%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .bento-section:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25), 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .bento-section:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .bento-body {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .bento-body { 
      flex-direction: column; 
      align-items: flex-start; 
    }
    .bento-icon { 
      margin-bottom: 1rem; 
    }
  }

  .bento-icon {
    width: 6rem;
    height: 6rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .bento-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .bento-body h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .bento-body p {
    color: rgb(209, 213, 219);
    line-height: 1.5;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  @keyframes spin-slow {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }
  .animate-spin-slow { animation: spin-slow 8s linear infinite; }
</style>
